# [English] Vehicle Parts, Inspections, and Repair Services Request for Standing Offer
## Notice Details

| Category | Detail |
| --- | --- |
| **Title** | Vehicle Parts, Inspections, and Repair Services Request for Standing Offer (WS4158664433-Doc4243780214) |
| **Release Date** | October 4, 2023 |
| **Offer Submission Deadline** | October 24, 2023, 2:00 PM |
| **Expected Contract Start Date** | N/A |
| **Expected Contract End Date** | September 25, 2025 |

## Procurement Details

*   **Category** (UNSPSC): 78181500 - Vehicle maintenance and repair services
*   **Method**: Competitive - Open bidding (Request for Standing Orders, Bid solicitation)
*   **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price
*   **Trade Agreements**: Canada Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
*   **Regions of Delivery**: Montréal, Canada
*   **Procuringentities**:

    *   **Contracting Entity**: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
    *   **Entity Address**: 11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage, Gatineau, Québec, K1A 0S5

## End-User Entities

*   **Entity Name**: Department of National Defence (DND)
*   **Address**: 101 Colonel By Dr, Ottawa, Ontario, K1A0K2 Canada

## Contact Information

*   **Name**: Melanie Caty (SPAC/PSPC)
*   **Email**: [melanie.caty@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca](mailto:melanie.caty@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca)
*   **Note**: For information only, if you are seeking more information related with this procurement, you are encourage to call the  BuyingTeam.

## Request Highlights

This Request for Standing Offer (RFSO) is a request for bids from companies to provide the delivery of vehicle parts, including inspection and repair services for the fleet of vehicles sold by Chrysler/Dodge and GM/Chevrolet.

All submissions are for contracts resulting in a single supply contract per stream. All Bidders are required to choose to either 

Stream 1: Dodge/Chevrolet Vehicles
Stream 2: Dodge/Chrysler Vehicles
Stream 3: GM/Chevrolet Vehicles

Each bidder is only allowed to tender to each of
